page.title: 12Housing
page.content: {1 Pound Cottages } Owned by the Prices,this house is about 190 years old and was extended 3 years ago. {2 Pound Cottages Owned by the Evans family and built of brick about 60 years ago. {3 Pound Cottages Owned by the Jones family it has been completly rebuilt and only a small amount of the original stonework is left. {4 Pound Cottages} This is the oldest of the cottages being about 200 years old.It is owned by the Synnock family and has only been altered slightly. More details are given on the following pages.
